# === WORKFLOW KIT START ===
# Workflow layer (selective tracking)
/ANTIGRAVITY.md
/AGENTS.md
/GEMINI.md

# Exclude duplicated engine/tool copies
/ai-workflow/scripts/
/ai-workflow/skills/
/ai-workflow/workflow_kit/
/ai-workflow/mcp_servers/
/ai-workflow/schemas/
/ai-workflow/templates/
/ai-workflow/examples/
/ai-workflow/global-snippets/
/ai-workflow/harnesses/
/ai-workflow/tests/

# Keep the data (memory) and core guides
!/ai-workflow/README.md
!/ai-workflow/WORKFLOW_INDEX.md
!/ai-workflow/core/
!/ai-workflow/memory/active/
# === WORKFLOW KIT END ===

# === CATALOG BUILD ARTIFACTS ===
# skill-discover 가 빌드하는 캐시 (CI / 로컬에서 매번 재생성)
skills/.index.json

# === PYTHON CACHES ===
# Python 3 가 scripts/*.py 의 .pyc 바이트코드를 캐시 (skills/_frontmatter.py,
# skill-lint, skill-discover 가 import 시). 빌드 산출물이므로 git 추적 차단.
# `**/__pycache__/` 패턴으로 모든 디렉터리의 __pycache__/ 매칭.
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
